## 6) Tools and Integrations

| Tool/Service | Used For | Integration Type | Executable vs Autonomy |
|---|---|---|---|
| LLM Service | intent extraction, summarization, message drafting | API | workflow-invoked with policy constraints |
| Scheduling System | slot lookup, booking, rescheduling, follow-up windows | REST/FHIR/GraphQL | automated after user confirmation |
| EHR / Provider Dashboard | encounter status, context, summary display | FHIR/HL7/API | event-triggered + provider-verified |
| Notification Provider | push/SMS/email reminders and alerts | API/Webhook | automated dispatch via preferences |
| Maps/Traffic API | travel estimates and departure guidance | REST API | recommendation only |
| Transportation Integration | ride options/deep links | API/Deep link | user-verified |
| Event Bus | lifecycle event processing | Stream/Queue | core automation backbone |
| Workflow Orchestrator | long-running flows, retries, compensations | Workflow engine | automated + manual override |
| SQL Database | appointments, consent, workflow logs | SQL | system-managed transactions |
| Analytics Warehouse | KPIs, model feedback loops | ETL/ELT | batch + near-real-time |

### Notes on Constraints

```text
Constraints
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Latency: booking endpoints and reminders must meet SLA
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Quotas: external API rate limiting and budget controls
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Security: PHI minimization and scoped service credentials
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Reliability: idempotency, retries, dead-letter queues, replay
```

