## 8) Security, Governance, and Ethics

### Security and Compliance Controls

```text
Healthcare Security Controls
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Encryption in transit and at rest
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ RBAC/ABAC access controls
